title: Peking Chinese Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In addition to traditional Chinese vegetable dishes like the buddhist delight and kung pao bean curd, vegan diners can get mock meats in place of meat in many dishes. Cashew chicken, sweet & sour chicken, orange chicken, Szechwan shrimp, shrimp chop suey. Atmosphere is average, with booths, wooden paneling and Chinese decor.
